You're right.
Don't be a buzzkill.

37:52.103 --> 37:53.275
One thing at a time.

37:53.438 --> 37:54.906
Hey.

37:55.064 --> 37:56.691
Listen, do you guys hear that?

37:56.858 --> 37:58.405
[BIRDs sQuA\/\/KING]

37:58.568 --> 37:59.990
MITCH: Yup.

38:00.153 --> 38:01.575
We've been hearing it all day.

38:01.738 --> 38:04.912
Different species of birds all
making the exact same noise.

38:06.284 --> 38:09.333
Mitch thinks the birds are
developing a common tongue.

38:09.496 --> 38:11.965
You think the eagles
can talk to the finches.

38:12.123 --> 38:15.502
MITCH: Can talk to the skua,
can talk to the black-headed grosbeak.

38:16.836 --> 38:20.090
There are maybe 300
billion birds in the world.

38:20.256 --> 38:22.054
Imagine if they could
all talk to each other.

38:22.842 --> 38:26.517
If that's true, they could send a
message around the world and back.

38:28.389 --> 38:32.110
Let's just figure out a way
to get to Zambia, quick.

38:45.490 --> 38:47.709
CLAYTON: Look on
the bright side.

38:47.867 --> 38:49.710
Your hiring instincts are good.

38:50.912 --> 38:53.335
They found the Mother Cell.

38:53.498 --> 38:55.717
And they think they can
use it to make a cure.

39:01.214 --> 39:05.640
It's a shame they won't live
to find out if they're right.

39:10.390 --> 39:12.518
I'll make the call.
